{"tid":2287968,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"《原神》洩露玩家電話號碼　系統輸入帳戶 ID 即完整顯示","createTime":"2020-11-16T07:06:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-16T07:53:44.000Z","uid":105822,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c3fcb87443b8bf9f0a43102af189ae0e6bedd4c6","tid":2287968,"uid":105822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T07:06:23.000Z","msg":"原神粉應該又突然間隻眼盲左<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n=====================<br />\n中國遊戲公司米哈遊一直以來均飽受各種爭議，而自推出《原神》以來，更被多次質疑其資訊安全管理措施，最近就有網民發現，《原神》官網在近幾周外洩了一批玩家的電話號碼。<br />\n<br />\n早在 10 月，Reddit 上已有用戶發帖表示，在《原神》官網使用「忘記密碼」系統試圖找回密碼時，發現如選擇「電話認證」確認身分，系統竟會完整顯示其電話號碼，故嘗試隨機輸入幾個用戶 ID，發現系統的而且確會完整顯示用戶的電話號碼，即只要擁有其他玩家的帳戶 ID，即可查閱到該些玩家的電話號碼。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/11/16/genshin-phone-number/game-channel/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F11%2F16%2Fgenshin-phone-number%2Fgame-channel%2F&d=fL1pPRntFf1zvvLBqslw3v7iMF%2BZ1QNuv%2BvReNsMrP0%3D&h=f48a9053\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/11/16/genshin-phone-number/game-channel/</a>"},{"pid":"91c9264f09c7cf9890cab3ea2e020f6e6f5be0b8","tid":2287968,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T07:10:07.000Z","msg":"支那豬先會玩支那遊戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁唔重視私隱就抵你死"},{"pid":"8d2f521932ebb500d182b3f8b84f9190877c34e5","tid":2287968,"uid":127425,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T07:10:34.000Z","msg":"棄驚了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b86642d64bf74b1029e1ad4cc06e2fc805dcdb66","tid":2287968,"uid":9049,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T07:16:00.000Z","msg":"棄驚保平安"},{"pid":"c33c5dd528ea75081c626ab7a76e87e2b5e20ef6","tid":2287968,"uid":80164,"like":